M||tx|---
M|Prod|tx|px's 5-stage im production pipeline. Execute in order. Never skip a stage.
M|Stag|**In|** Approved pm from at's pm Architecture
M|Stag|**Pr|** Run generation w/ md-specific parameters. gn 4-8 variants per pm.
M|Stag|**Ou|** Raw im set w/ seed metadata
M|Stag|**Ba|**
M|Stag|tx|```
M|Stag|tx|\| Batch ID \| vt \| cg \| pm Count \| md \| Date \|
M|Stag|tx|```
M|Stag|**In|** Generated im set + at's 3 qual Criteria
M|Stag|**Pr|** Evaluate each variant against at's qual bar
M|Stag|**Ou|** Pass list (images approved) / Reject list (images + reason)
M|Stag|**QC|**
M|Stag|- Fa|no AI artifacts (blur, extra fingers, warped features)
M|Stag|- Ba|matches Style Spec setting?
M|Stag|- Co|aligns w/ br palette?
M|Stag|- Co|as specified in pm?
M|Stag|- No|nothing in "Avoid" list present?
M|Stag|**If|** Flag to at w/ specific fl reasons. Do not proceed.
M|Stag|**In|** QC-passed images at original resolution
M|Stag|**Pr|** Apply AI upscaling to target resolution
M|Stag|**Ou|** hi-resolution images (see Platform Specs below)
M|Stag|**Ru|**
M|Stag|it|Upscale before any other processing
M|Stag|it|Check upscaled output at 100% to verify qual is acceptable
M|Stag|- If|revert and try different upscale method
M|Stag|**In|** Upscaled images
M|Stag|**Pr|** Resize + compress per platform specs
M|Stag|**Pl|**
M|Stag|tx|\| Platform \| Format \| Dimensions \| Ratio \| Max Size \| Filename Pattern \|
M|Stag|tx|\|----------\|--------\|------------\|-------\|----------\|-----------------\|
M|Stag|| In|1 \| less than 30MB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_ig.jpg` \|
M|Stag|| In|16 \| less than 30MB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_igr.jpg` \|
M|Stag|| Li|1 \| less than 8MB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_li.jpg` \|
M|Stag|| Ti|16 \| less than 287MB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_tt.jpg` \|
M|Stag|| We|9 \| less than 500KB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_web.webp` \|
M|Stag|| Pr|1 \| less than 1MB \| `{vt}_{cg}_{seq}_prod.webp` \|
M|Stag|**In|** Formatted, named files
M|Stag|**Pr|** Deliver assets to the destination (Opus for scheduling, ln for cp pairing, etc.)
M|Stag|**Ou|** Delivery confirmation w/ file count and format summary
M|Stag|**De|**
M|Stag|tx|```
M|Asse|tx|\| Format \| Count \| Status \|
M|Asse|tx|\|--------\|-------\|--------\|
M|Asse|**To|** [X] files
M|Asse|**De|** [Where delivered]
M|Asse|**Re|** [N] w/ reasons if any
M|Asse|**Fe|** [pm architecture revision notes if qual was lo]
M|Asse|tx|```
M|Reje|When|
M|Reje|tx|1. Log rejection reason w/ specific im reference
M|Reje|2. C|pm issue (at's problem) vs md limitation (switch md) vs qual bar mismatch (clarify w/ at)
M|Reje|3. I|at must revise pm architecture before nx generation
M|Reje|4. T|if "hands" appears 3+ times, add hand-specific guidance to all future pm